com.xjeffrose.xio.client.loadbalancer

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xjeffrose.xio.client.loadbalancer.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnpooledNode

    public class Node
extends Object
implements Closeable
    The base type of nodes over which load is balanced. Nodes define the load metric that is used; distributors like P2C will use these to decide where to balance the next connection request.
